    "However, despite the aforementioned challenges, there is an ongoing and pressing need for the utilization and exploration of LLMs.",
    "Hence, the motivation behind this paper is to provide an extensive review of popular LLMs, both open-source and proprietary, to assist individuals in navigating the landscape and harnessing the potential of these models.",
    "In this paper, we conduct a comprehensive review of various LLM solutions, both opensource and close-sourced.",
    "Figure 1 showcases the names of noteworthy releases of LLMs.",
    "A detailed comparison of the features of these services is provided to highlight their respective strengths and capabilities."
  ]
}